author: ggolden
msg: Removed storage of Profile from User getTemp, replaced in the JetspeedRunData.
The Profile is computed for each request and stored in the run data.
Storing a profile in the getTemp (i.e. the HTTP session) introduces a conflict
when more than one window is open in the session to more than one portal page.

author: ggolden
msg: Moved the portlet setID() call from the toolkit to the factory service
to be sure that a portlet  from the portlet factory always has an ID set.
